# Miscellanea: epub

# ## epub file format

# - Rename .epub to .zip and uncompress is
# - Check images, resize, optimize...

# To recompress the directory into a new book.epub:
cd epub-contents# The file mimetype must go first and uncompressedzip -X0 book.epub mimetype# Add the rest excluding trashzip -rDX9 book.epub * -x "*.DS_Store" -x mimetype

# You're done!

